name: Colon Cancer Ribbon of Hope Art
description: This is my genesis NFT. I've never minted anything before now and am very excited for this opportunity to bring awareness and raise funds to support the cancer community.  Proceeds from the sale of this NFT will go directly to The Cancer Show nonprofit organization. Please check out my YouTube Channel and FaceBook Page THE CANCER SHOW for more information, inspiration and insight. Artwork created by the amazing artist Victoria Fuller and designed with love by me. Thank you for your support!
